### Create User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "level": 1,
  "experience": 0,
  "gold": 100
}

### Get User by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users/1

### Get All Users
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users

### Update User (with DB lock)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "username": "testuser_updated",
  "email": "updated@example.com",
  "level": 5,
  "experience": 1000,
  "gold": 500
}

### Add Gold to User (with DB lock)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users/1/add-gold?amount=100

### Delete User
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/users/1

### Test concurrent gold addition (run multiple times quickly)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users/1/add-gold?amount=50
